---
title: Mexican Black Bean and Buckwheat Bake with Sour Cream
description: The star of tonight’s dish is ultra nutritious, super tasty buckwheat! Buckwheat is actually a seed related to rhubarb. It has a delicious, nutty flavour and is absolutely chock full of nutrition.
